<!-- Pickup & Delivery Program -->
<h2>Free Fleet Pickup &amp; Delivery Program</h2>
<p>Downtime costs money. That is why we built our pickup and delivery program to minimize the time your vehicles spend off the road. Here is exactly how it works:</p>
<ol class="pickup-steps">
<li><strong>Request a pickup</strong> — Call <a href="tel:+13125971286" style="color:var(--gold)">(312) 597-1286</a> or submit an <a href="/estimate/" style="color:var(--gold)">online estimate</a>. Tell us how many vehicles, what type, and your preferred pickup window.</li>
<li><strong>We schedule around your fleet</strong> — Early morning (6 AM), evening, and weekend pickups available. We work around your dispatch schedule so trucks are never pulled during peak hours.</li>
<li><strong>Our driver picks up your vehicle</strong> — A fully insured driver arrives at your yard, lot, or jobsite. We photograph the vehicle's condition before transport.</li>
<li><strong>Wrap installation at our shop</strong> — Your vehicle is wrapped in our climate-controlled, 70°F facility under LED lighting for perfect adhesion and color accuracy. Typical turnaround: 1–3 business days depending on vehicle size.</li>
<li><strong>Quality inspection &amp; photos</strong> — Every wrap is inspected by a second technician. We photograph the completed wrap from every angle and send you a preview before delivery.</li>
<li><strong>Free return delivery</strong> — We deliver the wrapped vehicle back to your location, clean and ready to hit the road. You receive care instructions and your 2-year warranty card.</li>
</ol>
<p>For fleets of <strong>5+ vehicles</strong>, we stagger pickups so you never lose more than one or two trucks from service at a time. We have wrapped entire fleets of 30+ vehicles with zero missed routes.</p>
